{
    "id": "firstaid/learn-cpr",
    "title": "Practice Basic CPR",
    "description": "Practice 30:2 compressions on a CPR manikin using nitrile gloves, a pocket mask and antiseptic wipes from your first aid kit. Confirm the area is safe, call emergency services first and sanitize gear after. This exercise does not replace formal certification.",
